name: Headless Chickens
overview: In a recognizable world of madness, the world of elite soccer, young footballers become rich and famous overnight with little idea of how to manage it, and cheeky people try to make a living out of it.

episodes.name: 24 Hours
episodes.overview: After his first success as a sports manager is upended by powerful rival Martinelli, former footballer Beto Martin desperately tries to save his struggling agency.

episodes.name: Nardinho and Me
episodes.overview: Against all odds, Beto becomes manager to the demanding Nardinho, and quickly learns how to deal with the football megastar’s ego – and various controversies.

episodes.name: Warm Up, You're Coming Out
episodes.overview: Despite refusing to participate in Nardinho’s bachelor party shenanigans, Beto finds his sobriety threatened by his oldest client and friend, Fran “el Toro” Verlarde.

episodes.name: Yes, No
episodes.overview: Agency employees Cristina, Mario, and Armando speculate over the lead-up to Beto and Miguel’s explosive fight.

episodes.name: Beto, Sonia, and the Magical Shoes
episodes.overview: Beto’s romantic weekend escape with his girlfriend Sonia is disrupted by his daughters and a menacing visitor.

episodes.name: The Aquarium
episodes.overview: With the help of Sonia, Miguel, and an old friend, Beto gradually reconstructs the day leading up to the car crash.
